spine-bashing
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:lying in bed (flat on one's back)
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:cf. Maori PT
Pronunciation:
Notes: ca1944 (WW2) L. Cleveland
Citations
